    "en": {
      "name": "D/D Count Surveyor",
      "effect": "You can discard 1 other \"D/D\" monster; Special Summon this card from your hand. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can add 1 \"D/D\" monster with 0 ATK or DEF from your Deck to your hand. You can only use each monster effect of \"D/D Count Surveyor\" once per turn.",
      "pendulumEffect": "Once per turn, if you Pendulum Summon a \"D/D/D\" monster(s): You can target 3 monsters your opponent controls with the same Type or Attribute as each other; Tribute 2 of those 3 face-up monsters, and if you do, the other gains ATK/DEF equal to the total ATK/DEF the Tributed monsters had on the field.",
      "official": false
    },
